0.body: Venture Index is an attempt to index the Philippines local startup ecosystem. Coverage Our current goal is to index the following: Online communities Upcoming and ongoing events Recruitment platforms Service providers Startup resources Contribution This website's entire source code is publicly available on our GitHub Repository . To suggest an edit, just click the top-right edit button of the page you want to edit. We use the Markdown syntax to write our pages. Submitting your proposed changes will create a "pull-request". Once approved by us, your proposed changes will be immediately reflected in our website. You may check our repository's GitHub Actions tab to view the latest build progress and status. Your ideas, feedback, and suggestions are welcome at our repository's GitHub Issues tab. Thank you.
